Package: TANGOQTL
Type: Package
Title: Trans-Regulatory Adaptive Network Gene-Set Omnibus Tests
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Yifan Zhang
Maintainer: Yifan Zhang <NA>
Description: Implements TANGO, an adaptive omnibus testing framework for trans-QTL module mapping. The method combines dense burden, variance-component, sparse MinP, and optional network-smoothed evidence for SNP-module association testing.
